(1120, 0, 1, 18247, 20993, '', '', 148, '', 10, '2019-01-21', '14:00', '<p>Trial Rimula R4X 15W-40&nbsp;Forklift MHI (mitsubishi)</p>', '<p>customer want to do trial&nbsp;to seek durabilty/ performance Rimula R4X, setting 750 H as max trial terget.</p>\n<p>based 500 H lab result oil condition it''s still ok and can be extend more. so today is taking sample for 763 H. for sampling snd to SGS lab</p>', '<p>Submit sample to SGS</p>', ''),
(1121, 0, 1, 7607, 8702, '', '', 148, '', 2, '2019-01-29', '10:00', '<p>Bp Nando. can''t meet cz he at shift 2</p>\n<p>Bp Agung. can''t meet cz have meetings</p>\n<p>Bp Ihsan. Purchasing, PE (maintenance), HR for Refrigerator BU.</p>\n<p>Collecting data DVR</p>\n<p>Issue filter blocking at unit Injection M-01 Mitsubishi 850 MG</p>\n<p>They asking lab test for help them for audit data</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p>DVR Corena S4 R 46 used for vacuum machine for Compressor refrigerator unit line. we cant&nbsp;collect data cz Bp Ihsan is not in charge for maintenance details.</p>\n<p>Based informastion we get in unit M-01 injection Mitsubishi 850MG have issue filter blocking only this unit, topup frequency 20L/ week. they using Idemitsu since 2004-2017 without flushing. at july 2017 they do total flushing with 12 drum Shell Tellus MX 46.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>taking sampling for unit injection Mitsubishi 850 MG (double oil filter) &amp; 450 MG (Single oil filter).</p>\n<p>other information, user at panasonic more care about periodic oil change, unit they have is relative old.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Production 50 pcs/Hours.</p>\n<p>Other product can we offer Rimula&gt;Generator, Corene&gt;Compressor (2 unit),</p>', '<p>Submit sample to Petrolab.</p>\n<p>in next discussion make sure can meet with bp Nando do interpretation lab result, collect DVR data &amp; detail others oil they need.</p>', '');
